creator: Klick and Pap Services

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Immediate clearance of the 'new orders' list when the new ones have been acted on.
Distinction between ASAP & Scheduled while accepting.
Fixed notifications.
Better progress updates while processing request
Notifications in every step of the order - placement, payment, reception confirmation, etc
-Completed orders summary - track what you've successfully served
-Quick summary of new/delivered orders
-Detailed view of all orders(ASAP, Scheduled /Processing/Rejected)
